highlights.text: “Girls Want Girls (with Lil Baby)” by Drake and Lil Baby is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 240 weeks straight.
“OUT OUT (feat. Charli XCX & Saweetie)” by Joel Corry, Jax Jones, Charli XCX, and Saweetie is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 49 spots at #87.
Drake has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Girls Want Girls (with Lil Baby)” is the highest at #2.
